physical and mental and emotional abuse I was told every day that I was a mistake and that I was worthless and I was garbage and I was beaten very badly on the daily basis and there was prostitution and drug dealing and all sorts of just unhealthiness and I grew up with that hole inside of me you know I just for a long time I believed that I was worthless and

